            <title>[LU-17989] Cleanup use of fake interface in sanity-lnet</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17989</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;All callers of have_interface() are using it to check that setup_fakeif() completed successfully, so setup_fakeif() should just do this itself.&lt;/p&gt;

